beer.beer_description: Walker Imperial Pils. On September 18, 2012 Chuck Norris, after a relaxing trip into space, he returned from a spacecraft into Earth's atmosphere diving, reaching a temperature of 3000 ° F. The impact swept Europe, leaving intact only a field of Saaz in the Czech Republic and Codogno to allow Brewfist and Pubs all'Arrogant to create this beautiful Pils.

items.checkin_comment: [RB 3.6 13/09/14] Blonde légèrement dorée, col de mousse blanche et crémeuse moyen. Nez de caramel, d’herbes, de citron et de pomme. Bouche de caramel et de houblon saaz : herbes et épices. Amertume moyenne. Très bonne pils.

items.badge_description:
On October 22nd, we’re celebrating Untappd’s 13th anniversary! ?

Thank you to each and every one of you for making this beautifully diverse community what it is today! So raise your glasses, check in a beer, earn a badge, and cheers to another lucky 13.

Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
